Clinical Scientific Computing # The Clinical Scientific Computing (CSC) team at
University College Hospital London (UCLH) supports clinical research, analytics, and computational infrastructure across the organisation.
We work closely with clinicians, researchers, and IT to deliver secure, reproducible, and scalable computing solutions.
